<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="addition-n">addition <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'dɪʃn/    美 /ə'dɪʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 加法；增加：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The sign " + " stands for addition. 
符号“＋”代表加法。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The expenses of the household, <strong>with the addition of</strong> a second child, were heavy.
多了个孩子，家庭开销大了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] 增加的人 / 物；附加物：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I love roses, and I think they make a beautiful <strong>addition to</strong> any garden. 
我喜欢玫瑰，我认为它们可以给任何花园增添姿色。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-addition">in addition</h3>
<p>1.<strong>另外；加之：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The company provides cheap Internet access. In addition, it makes shareware freely available. 
该公司提供廉价的互联网接入服务。此外，它还免费提供共享软件。</p></div>

<h3 id="in-addition-to">in addition to</h3>
<p>1.<strong>除…之外 (还)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In addition to reading for knowledge, we read for fun and inspiration.
我们读书除了为获取知识外，还为得到乐趣和灵感。</p><footer>2014 浙江书面表达</footer></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>additional   /ə'dɪʃənl/ adj <br />
additionally [ə'dɪʃənəli] adv   </p>
<h2 id="_4">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>In addition<strong><em>_</em></strong>_the school, the village has a clinic, which was also built with government support.  （2014 天津改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. to  </p></div>